snippet.title: Mario In Clock Town (V1.1) - SM64 Rom Hack (Release Trailer)
snippet.description:
Mario crosses over into the world of Termina! Collect all of the Power Stars (each one based on a Mask or item from Majora's Mask) and stop Bowser from destroying Termina with Majora's Mask!

Created For Simpleflip's SM64 Crossover Competition

Download Links:

Direct Download (Comes with bps patch, Flips, Pictures, and Changelog.) - 
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1evz5Z4MgsiuXUY7j28mPbOlMhw7boD-4/view?usp=sharing

https://romhacking.com/hack/Mario-In-Clock-Town
